version_description:
Thank you for using the TEC app! To provide you with a high quality app that keeps on improving, we regularly upload updates to the App Store.
These updates include improvements to the reliability and speed of the TEC app.

Download the latest version to see the latest functionalities available in the TEC app.

Thank you for using the TEC app! In order to offer you an application of the highest quality and performance, we regularly publish updates in the App Store.

In addition to improvements for reliability and speed of the TEC app, this new update includes:
- Integration of the new WEL lines of TEC;
- “Earlier”/ “Later” options on line search;
- The “MOBI-ESPACE TEC” sales channel in the point of sale search.

Download the latest version to see the latest functionalities available in the TEC app.
